# Note that you'll need a recent version in order for this to work, the version
# you get when you `apt install ncmpcpp` will probably be too old for this
# config. You'll also need to enable 256 colors in your terminal (this is done
# by adding a line in your .bashrc). For the whole config file check out the
# project's github: https://github.com/ncmpcpp/ncmpcpp/blob/master/doc/config

# Setup
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
